    "In addition, ML is used to predict transportation times and improve moves as well as the allocation of storage locations.",
    "Although a strict digital twin is not applied, there is already a (near) real time integration of data with a model-based approach for manual dispatching.",
    "A key benefit is the better use of resources described by port stakeholders.",
    "The implementation of automated processes based on the digital model in Bremen has resulted in several improvements in terms of reducing search orders for misplaced items and automatically recording and storing precise location data, which were previously completed manually.",
    "However, with the introduction of automated processes and the ability to track the exact locations of goods, search orders for misplaced items have become rare."
